articles.title: Next-generation emergency response service launches with AI, GPS technology
articles.description: KUALA LUMPUR: Next Generation Emergency Response Services 999 (NG MERS 999), Malaysia's new emergency communication infrastructure, developed through a collaboration between Telekom Malaysia Berhad (TM) and the Communications Ministry, launches on Sunday (Nov 16). In a statement, TM said NG MERS 999 was developed to replace the MERS 999 system, which was also developed and operated by TM.
